<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM2.10">
<l>allimāmalar maṅkaināta ṉaraṅkaṉmeyyaṭi yārkaḷtam</l>
<l>ellaiyillaṭi maittiṟattiṉi leṉṟumēvu maṉattaṉām</l>
<l>kollikāvalaṉ kūṭalnāyakaṉ kōḻikkōṉkula cēkaraṉ</l>
<l>colliliṉṟamiḻ mālaivallavar toṇṭartoṇṭarka ḷāvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master the sweet Tamil garland in the words of Kulacēkaraṉ,</l>
<l rend="indent">the guardian of Kolli, the master of Kūṭal, the king of Kōḻi,</l>
<l rend="indent">who has a heart that dwells forever in the state of limitless servitude of the true</l>
<l rend="indent">servants of Raṅga, the Lord of the Woman on the big lotus blossom,</l>
<l>shall become the servants’ servants.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
